Early Careers

   Being a worldwide digital leader we have many exciting and challenging
   programs and opportunities for you, in a wide variety of fields of
   expertise.

Diversity

   Diversity and inclusion are embedded in our DNA.  With robust programs
   in place to support our 5 Diversity Dimensions (Gender, Accessibility,
   LGBT, Generations, and Culture) our 120,000 global employees are
   encouraged to contribute to our culture of inclusivity.

Culture

   Our company culture is created every day by all of the self-motivated,
   committed professionals who work here. Our core values are important to
   us and expressed in the way we work with each other and with our
   clients.

Our Expertise

   Big Data & Security – we create competitive advantage for our clients
   from big data, and ensure data is delivered safely and securely to the
   right parties.

   Business & Platform Solutions – we transform strategic approaches to
   technology, combining innovative solutions with established ones.

   Digital Payments and e-Transactions – through Worldline, we provide
   unrivalled leadership in expert solutions for the fast- changing
   payment and digital services market.

   Infrastructure & Data Management – we create business benefits through
   intelligently managed IT and digital services.

   Unified Communication & Collaboration – at Unify, we combine voice,
   data and video, to help our customers benefit from a unique
   collaboration experience.

   The Olympic Games - the greatest sporting spectacle on the planet.
    Powered by innovative digital services. Delivered by us.

   If you would like to read more about Atos, please click below to visit
   our corporate website where you can read about our services, products,
   brands, and much more.
